beIN SPORTS XTRA 5.desc: دوري أبطال أفريقيا، هي مسابقة كرة قدم سنوية للأندية ينظمها الاتحاد الأفريقي لكرة القدم (CAF) وتتنافس عليها أندية الدرجة الأولى الأفريقية.
beIN SPORTS XTRA 5.title_fr: FC Lupopo (RDC) vs Mamelodi Sundowns FC (RSA) - Ligue des Champions de la CAF 2025/26 MD5
beIN SPORTS XTRA 5.desc_en: The CAF Champions League, is an annual club football competition organized by the Confederation of African Football (CAF) and contested by top-division African clubs. It is the most prestigious club competition in African football and is live and exclusive only on beIN. The current champions are Pyramids Football Club from Egypt.
beIN SPORTS XTRA 5.desc_fr: La Ligue des champions de la CAF est une compétition annuelle de football interclubs organisée par la Confédération africaine de football (CAF) et disputée par les clubs africains de première division.

beIN SPORTS XTRA 5.desc: الدوري الإسباني 2 هو قسم كرة القدم الاحترافي الثاني للرجال في نظام الدوري الإسباني لكرة القدم.
beIN SPORTS XTRA 5.title_fr: Cadix vs Almeria - LaLiga Hypermotion 2025-2026 - La liga 2 espagnole
beIN SPORTS XTRA 5.desc_en: La Liga 2 is the men's second professional association football division of the Spanish football league system. It is contested by 22 teams, with the top two teams plus the winner of a play-off promoted to La Liga and replaced by the three lowest-placed teams in that division.
beIN SPORTS XTRA 5.desc_fr: La Liga 2 est la deuxième division masculine de football professionnel du système de ligue de football espagnol.

beIN 4K.original_title: Tottenham Hotspur vs. Manchester City - English Premier League 2026/2027
beIN 4K.title: توتنهام هوتسبر ضد مانشستر سيتي - الدوري الإنجليزي الممتاز 2026/2027
beIN 4K.desc: سجل أنطوان سيمينيو لاعب مانشستر سيتي خمسة أهداف في آخر ثماني مباريات له في الدوري الإنجليزي الممتاز، وهو أكبر عدد من الأهداف من أي لاعب في هذا الإطار الزمني.
beIN 4K.title_fr: Tottenham Hotspur contre Manchester City - Premier League anglaise 2026/2027
beIN 4K.desc_en: Man City’s Antoine Semenyo has scored five goals in his last eight Premier League appearances, the joint most of any player in that timeframe. One of those was a late winner against Spurs for Bournemouth in January, with only Eric Cantona in 1992-93  and Benito Carbone in 1999-00  scoring against Spurs for two teams in a single season. Omar Marmoush netted his first Premier League goal of the season in Man City’s 2-0 win over Wolves but all eight of his goals in the competition have been scored at home – he’s failed to score with all 20 of his attempts in 12 games away from home.
beIN 4K.desc_fr: Antoine Semenyo de Man City a marqué cinq buts lors de ses huit dernières apparitions en Premier League, soit le plus grand nombre de joueurs au cours de cette période.

beIN 4K.title_fr: Aryna Sabalenka vs Elena Rybakina - Jour 14 - Finale Simple Femmes - Session du soir - Rod Laver Are
